re'; surmounted by Christian monogram, and outlined by a small timpanum. An 'imperfetta copia' was made, on a limestone block, or the inscr. when it was still in better condition, and this now in the Museo Iudica coll. Only line 3 still readable on original, having: teleuta eteleutese eton-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>42.0820.4\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Pugliese Carratelli\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1956\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>no.48 ph\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/PJDRZH66\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001394\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001394\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"NSA\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Pugliese Carratelli\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Ctitle>NSA\u003C/title>\n                        \u003Cdate>1953\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>350\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1992\u003C/d